### Food Recognition API - Upload and Analyze

### Upload food image for analysis
POST http://localhost:8000/ai/agent/upload
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="food1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\food1.png
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="userId"

1
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="notes"

Salad for lunch
--WebAppBoundary--

###
